==========what is database trigger?
Set of operations that is run when specific actions occur within a Database.

==========what is Apex Trigger?
Apex code that is run when specific actions occur within a salesforce object.

==========Apex  supports triggers before and after follwing events:
-Insert
-Update
-Delete
-Merge
-Upsert
-Undelete
==========Why do we need Apex Trigger?
helpful in automating business processes.

trigger LeadTrigger on Lead (before insert, before update) {
	System.debug('Lead trigger called');
}
